OL,3,CSolong container ship that crashed in
OL,4,CNorth Sea arrives in Aberdeen
OL,6,FThe Solong's captain, Vladimir Motin,
OL,7,F59, from St Petersburg, Russia,
OL,8,Fappeared at the Old Bailey charged
OL,9,Fwith gross negligence manslaughter and
OL,10,Fwas remanded in custody.
OL,12,FHe is due to stand trial in January
OL,13,F2026.
OL,15,FIt was accompanied by a vessel with
OL,16,Fcounter-pollution measures as it
OL,17,Farrived at the Port of Aberdeen at
OL,18,Faround 7am on Friday.
