OL,6,F"Solong will be under tow by one tug
OL,7,Fand accompanied by another tug, plus a
OL,8,Fvessel with counter-pollution measures
OL,9,Fshould they be required. Tug and tow
OL,10,Fare scheduled to arrive at Aberdeen.
OL,12,F"The Stena Immaculate remains in a
OL,13,Fstable condition with salvage
OL,14,Fongoing," he added.
