OL,6,FKing's Lynn and West Norfolk Council
OL,7,Fsaid it had begun removing the
OL,8,Fnurdles, focusing initially on the
OL,9,Fstretch of beaches between Holme-next-
OL,10,Fthe-Sea and Old Hunstanton.
OL,12,F"HM Coastguard continues to support
OL,13,Flocal authorities which are leading
OL,14,Fthe onshore response to pollution,
OL,15,Fincluding plastic nurdles, in Norfolk
OL,16,Fand Lincolnshire," Mr O'Callaghan
OL,17,Fadded.
OL,19,F"HM Coastguard will continue to keep
OL,20,Fthe overall situation under close
OL,21,Freview."
